{"tid":368513,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 一日要餵幾多貓糧?","createTime":"2017-08-21T15:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T04:04:16.000Z","uid":52377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9786ef31c0406b793fc3cc9a244a2df16c36c798","tid":368513,"uid":52377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:06:26.000Z","msg":"買左神級糧Orijen比主人食, 但好似食到有肚腩仔, 岩岩上佢官網睇左佢指南但睇唔明有無巴打可以幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/225641_a2ef48a41ceaf18fbd16cd3e0ff4b162.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F225641_a2ef48a41ceaf18fbd16cd3e0ff4b162.png&h=e45992b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主人3個月大, 重1.4kg, 咁一日要比幾多佢食?<br />\n佢指引話斷奶後 就餵1/2cup per 身體體重, 但唔明大概要餵幾多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主人j圖一張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/21/230553_585001a704fd3febe9b69883a6a1c910.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F21%2F230553_585001a704fd3febe9b69883a6a1c910.jpeg&h=c22a689f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc269ead55b0094236e2146457600826ac9ff507","tid":368513,"uid":31475,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"肥d可愛d<br />\n放係度<br />\n佢想食就自然會去食"},{"pid":"b08d3be96ad41dc4628cbd729172001f544f26bf","tid":368513,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"我6個月前任佢食"},{"pid":"78179854cd27d4e521af0346c9e872bd74a6ed72","tid":368513,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥d可愛d<br />\n放係度<br />\n佢想食就自然會去食</blockquote><br />\n咁就一定肥到痴線"},{"pid":"83b2193